entries.femaleVariant: My mother fought in the war. Never talked about it – not even once.
Who was leading Arasaka? Was it Yorinobu?
You joking? Back then, Yorinobu didn't want anything to do with his father's empire.
Orders trickled down from Kei Arasaka. At least – officially.
Not a lot of people these days remember – Saburo had two sons.
And so the world keeps turning.
